init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The "Dad" mugs are replaced with "Dad" mugs that are actually the correct ranking of Dads.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I found myself thinking about how much I loved my dad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I didn't want to make him feel bad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I searched the kitchen, the living room, the dining room, and the basement.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Umm, I was just looking for something," I said.
